---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const today = new Date();
const formattedDate = `${today.toLocaleString('en-US', { month: 'long' })} ${today.getDate()}, ${today.getFullYear()}`;
---

<Layout 
  title="Privacy Policy | RecycleOldTech.com"
  description="Learn how RecycleOldTech.com collects, uses, and protects your information when you visit our website."
>
  <div class="bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12 max-w-4xl mt-16">
      <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl shadow-sm p-8 border border-gray-100">
        <div class="prose lg:prose-xl mx-auto">
          <h1 class="text-4xl font-display font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Privacy Policy</h1>
          
          <div class="inline-block bg-accent-50 text-accent-700 px-4 py-2 rounded-md mb-6">
            <p class="m-0"><strong>Effective Date:</strong> {formattedDate}</p>
          </div>
          
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700">At <strong class="text-accent-600">RecycleOldTech.com</strong>, your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you visit our website.</p>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-semibold text-gray-800 mt-8 mb-4">1. Information We Collect</h2>
        
        <p class="text-gray-700">We may collect certain non-personally identifiable information about your visit, including:</p>
        
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-gray-700 mb-6">
          <li>IP address</li>
          <li>Browser type and version</li>
          <li>Pages visited and time spent on site</li>
          <li>Referring website or source</li>
          <li>Location data (at the city/region level)</li>
          <li>Device type and operating system</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p class="text-gray-700 bg-gray-100 p-4 rounded-md border-l-4 border-accent-500">We do <strong class="text-accent-800">not</strong> collect any personally identifiable information unless you choose to provide it via a form submission (e.g., location search or contact form).</p>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-semibold text-gray-800 mt-8 mb-4">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        
        <p class="text-gray-700">We use the collected information to:</p>
        
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-gray-700 mb-6">
          <li>Improve the performance and functionality of our website</li>
          <li>Understand user behavior and traffic patterns</li>
          <li>Help connect users with certified electronics recycling centers</li>
          <li>Monitor and analyze the effectiveness of our content and tools</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-semibold text-gray-800 mt-8 mb-4">3. Analytics and Tracking</h2>
        
        <p class="text-gray-700">RecycleOldTech.com uses the following third-party tools:</p>
        
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-gray-700 mb-6">
          <li><strong class="text-accent-700">Google Analytics</strong> and/or <strong class="text-accent-700">Vercel Analytics</strong> to monitor website traffic and usage</li>
          <li><strong class="text-accent-700">Google AdSense</strong> to serve ads that may be relevant to your interests</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p class="text-gray-700">These tools may set cookies or collect usage data to help us better understand our visitors. You can disable cookies in your browser settings at any time.</p>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-semibold text-gray-800 mt-8 mb-4">4. Google AdSense and Advertising</h2>
        
        <p class="text-gray-700">We use <strong class="text-accent-700">Google AdSense</strong> to display advertisements on our website. This service uses cookies and similar technologies to:</p>
        
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-gray-700 mb-4">
          <li>Serve ads based on your visits to this site and other sites on the Internet</li>
          <li>Personalize advertising content and measure ad effectiveness</li>
          <li>Provide advertising-related services such as ad delivery, reporting, attribution, and security</li>
          <li>Prevent fraud and abuse</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Google and its partners may use cookies or device identifiers to show you ads based on your prior visits to our website or other websites. You can opt out of personalized advertising by visiting <a href="https://www.google.com/settings/ads" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-accent-600 hover:text-accent-800 underline">Google's Ad Settings</a>.</p>
        
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">You can learn more about how Google uses data here:<br />
        <a href="https://policies.google.com/technologies/ads" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-accent-600 hover:text-accent-800 underline">https://policies.google.com/technologies/ads</a></p>
        
        <h3 class="text-xl font-display font-semibold text-gray-800 mt-6 mb-4">Affiliate Disclosures</h3>
        
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">RecycleOldTech.com may participate in affiliate marketing programs. This means we may earn commissions from qualifying purchases made through links on our website. These affiliate relationships do not influence our editorial content or recommendations.</p>
        
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">We are committed to transparency and will always disclose when a link is an affiliate link. Our primary goal remains providing accurate, helpful information about electronics recycling regardless of any potential affiliate relationships.</p>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-semibold text-gray-800 mt-8 mb-4">5. GDPR and CCPA Compliance</h2>
        
        <h3 class="text-xl font-display font-semibold text-gray-800 mt-6 mb-4">General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR)</h3>
        
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">If you are a resident of the European Economic Area (EEA), you have certain data protection rights under the GDPR:</p>
        
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-gray-700 mb-4">
          <li><strong>Right of Access:</strong> You can request copies of your personal data</li>
          <li><strong>Right to Rectification:</strong> You can request correction of inaccurate personal data</li>
          <li><strong>Right to Erasure:</strong> You can request deletion of your personal data</li>
          <li><strong>Right to Restrict Processing:</strong> You can request restriction of processing of your personal data</li>
          <li><strong>Right to Data Portability:</strong> You can request transfer of your data to another service</li>
          <li><strong>Right to Object:</strong> You can object to processing of your personal data</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h3 class="text-xl font-display font-semibold text-gray-800 mt-6 mb-4">California Consumer Privacy Act (CCPA)</h3>
        
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">If you are a California resident, you have the following rights under the CCPA:</p>
        
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-gray-700 mb-4">
          <li><strong>Right to Know:</strong> You can request information about the categories and specific pieces of personal information we collect</li>
          <li><strong>Right to Delete:</strong> You can request deletion of your personal information</li>
          <li><strong>Right to Opt-Out:</strong> You can opt out of the sale of your personal information (we do not sell personal information)</li>
          <li><strong>Right to Non-Discrimination:</strong> We will not discriminate against you for exercising your privacy rights</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-semibold text-gray-800 mt-8 mb-4">6. Your Rights and Choices</h2>
        
        <p class="text-gray-700">To exercise any of these rights or make requests regarding your personal data, please <a href="/contact" class="text-accent-600 hover:text-accent-800 font-medium">contact us</a>. We will respond to your request within 30 days.</p>
        
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">You can also opt out of data collection through your browser settings or by visiting the opt-out links provided by our advertising partners.</p>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-semibold text-gray-800 mt-8 mb-4">7. Data Security</h2>
        
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your information. However, please note that no online transmission or storage system is 100% secure.</p>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-semibold text-gray-800 mt-8 mb-4">8. Third-Party Links</h2>
        
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">RecycleOldTech.com may contain links to third-party websites. We are not responsible for the content or privacy practices of those sites.</p>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-semibold text-gray-800 mt-8 mb-4">9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with a new effective date.</p>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-semibold text-gray-800 mt-8 mb-4">10. Contact Us</h2>
        
        <p class="text-gray-700">If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, feel free to reach out through our:</p>
        
        <div class="mt-4 mb-8">
          <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 border border-transparent text-base font-medium rounded-md shadow-sm text-white bg-accent-600 hover:bg-accent-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-accent-500 transition-colors">
            Contact Page
          </a>
        </div>
        
        <hr class="my-8 border-gray-200" />
        
        <p class="text-center text-lg font-medium text-accent-700 bg-accent-50 p-4 rounded-lg mt-8"><strong>Thank you for visiting RecycleOldTech.com and for doing your part to support responsible e-waste recycling.</strong></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</Layout> 
